WEBVTT

00:15:58.312 --> 00:16:01.532
There seems to be
no consequence whatsoever

00:16:01.532 --> 00:16:04.997
for attacks against
humanitarian aid workers.

00:16:04.997 --> 00:16:09.357
After my release, I was told
not to seek any form of justice.

00:16:09.357 --> 00:16:12.584
It won't do you any good,
that's what I was told.

00:16:12.584 --> 00:16:16.673
Plus, you're going to put in danger
the life of other colleagues.

00:16:17.723 --> 00:16:20.884
It took me years to see the sentencing

00:16:20.884 --> 00:16:25.175
of three people associated 
with my kidnapping,

00:16:25.175 --> 00:16:27.711
but this was the exception.

00:16:27.711 --> 00:16:32.230
There was no justice for any 
of the humanitarian aid workers